column2: SELECT   g.ObjId, g.ra, g.dec, g.field, g.type, g.clean, g.probPSF, g.insideMask, g.flags, g.psfMag_r, g.psfMagErr_r, g.cmodelMag_r, g.cmodelMagErr_r, g.PSFfwhm_r, p.z, p.zErr into mydb.MyTable from Galaxy as g     join Photoz as p on p.Objid = g.ObjId   where g.type=&&& and g.cmodelMag_r < &&& and g.insideMask = &&&
